           <span class="imgWrap"> <img src="http://www.buffalonews.com/storyimage/BN/20150217/CITYANDREGION/150219110/AR/0/AR-150219110.jpg&amp;maxW=602&amp;maxH=392&amp;AlignV=top" alt=""></span> 
